description: A cartoon duck wearing a smug, knowing expression is featured on a white background. The duck is bright yellow with round cheeks, a shiny head, and eyes that appear half closed. It has an orange beak and is holding a white cigarette or joint in its left hand. The tip of the cigarette is black, and wisps of gray smoke curl upwards from it. Above the duck in large purple lettering is the text "HAHA, CLASSIC". The duck's expression changes slightly, with its eyes briefly opening and closing.
